726020f-b.title: Queens: Springfield Boulevard - 76th Avenue
726020f-b.text:
Alley Park (Queens)I The area on the east side of Springfield
Boulevard, north of 76th Avenue. This property was owned by S.
Petrowsky in 1909.
P. L. Sperr  June 6, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2,3
